pero minti' e yolin tuc'il. Toj nim amb´il, a Harry n-chi kub´ tan n-ka´yin twitz
aju t-xaq qlolj te t-watbʼil. A ja te q´uqb´il mya b´a´n t-xilen,
ex, noqwit mintiʼxix in ximen tiʼj, otoq tzʼel tnikʼ Harry tiʼj qa
